Diana Millay https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diana_Millay 0 Diana Claire Millay (born June 7, 1935) is an American actress. She is best known for her work in television, having guest starred in close to one hundred prime time shows, both live and filmed, and for playing continuing roles on two daytime soap operas, Dark Shadows and The Secret Storm.
